OL,3,CDoes rugby union owe rugby league an
OL,4,Capology?
OL,6,FLucy Anderson reflects on her
OL,7,Fexclusive investigation into the
OL,8,Ftreatment of border rugby codebreakers.
OL,10,FDoes rugby union owe rugby league an
OL,11,Fapology?
OL,13,FAs someone born 5 years after rugby
OL,14,Funion turned professional, it seems an
OL,15,Fodd suggestion. They are two separate
OL,16,Fsports, with different fanbases and
OL,17,Ftheir own laws.
