OL,3,CDoes rugby union owe rugby league an
OL,4,Capology?
OL,6,FIt's stranger still to hear a borderer
OL,7,F- someone who grew up in Scottish
OL,8,Frugby union's heartland - appear to be
OL,9,Fsympathising with those who rebelled
OL,10,Fagainst 'our' game.
OL,12,FI've spent the last 6 months exploring
OL,13,Fthe forgotten feud between the two
OL,14,Fcodes, and why so many talented young
OL,15,Fmen left the Scottish Borders to play
OL,16,Fthe 'rival' code in the north of
OL,17,FEngland.
