OL,3,CDoes rugby union owe rugby league an
OL,4,Capology?
OL,6,FOn this journey I discovered the
OL,7,Fstories of 16 Border codebreakers, who
OL,8,Fhave been tucked away from our
OL,9,Fhistory. Banished from the clubs where
OL,10,Fthey honed their craft, and as a
OL,11,Fresult were excluded from the very
OL,12,Ffabric of our society.
OL,14,FRoots of rebellion: One game becomes
OL,15,Ftwo codes
OL,17,FToday the two games are so separate
OL,18,Fit's easy to forget they were once the
OL,19,Fsame sport.
