OL,3,CDoes rugby union owe rugby league an
OL,4,Capology?
OL,6,FAnd so rugby league was born, and
OL,7,Fbattle lines were drawn.
OL,9,FElsewhere in Britain, including here
OL,10,Fin the Scottish borders, union
OL,11,Fcontinued to dominate, played at an
OL,12,Famateur level. Governing bodies - like
OL,13,Fthe Scottish Rugby Union - laid down
OL,14,Fclear and harsh sanctions on this new
OL,15,Fcode. League was forbidden, and anyone
OL,16,Fseen to be associated with it would be
OL,17,Fbanned from playing, coaching and
OL,18,Fsocialising at union clubs.
