OL,6,FSpoiler - rugby union also became
OL,7,Fprofessional 100 years later in 1995.
OL,8,FWith their own move to
OL,9,Fprofessionalism, union essentially
OL,10,Fadmitted league was right to pay
OL,11,Fplayers.
OL,13,FI've only ever known both games to be
OL,14,Fprofessional, and this is probably
OL,15,Fwhat makes the treatment of
OL,16,Fcodebreakers during this period all
OL,17,Fthe more alien to me.
