OL,3,CDoes rugby union owe rugby league an
OL,4,Capology?
OL,6,FGrowing up in the Scottish Borders,
OL,7,Frugby (union) is religion.
OL,9,FThe border league is the oldest rugby
OL,10,Funion club competition in the world.
OL,11,FToday it's still king. Conversations
OL,12,Fin every workplace, home and exchange
OL,13,Fin the street in any border town often
OL,14,Frevolve around it.
OL,16,FWhether you're from Hawick, Kelso or
OL,17,FGalashiels - you're brought up knowing
OL,18,Fyou're from a rugby town. Each just a
OL,19,Fstones throw from the English border,
OL,20,Fand yet we feel all the more Scottish
OL,21,Ffor it. It's a pretty unique existence.
