OL,6,FAs spectator numbers dwindle on
OL,7,Ftouchlines across Britain, each
OL,8,FSaturday you'll find stands here
OL,9,Fpacked like the church pews of a
OL,10,Fforgotten era.
OL,12,FThere are fierce rivalries between us,
OL,13,Fbut at the same time we are all
OL,14,Fborderers with the same hereditary
OL,15,Flove of the game.
