OL,3,CDoes rugby union owe rugby league an
OL,4,Capology?
OL,6,FI knew some of my schoolfriend's
OL,7,Fgranddad's had played rugby
OL,8,Fprofessionally over the border. But
OL,9,Fthere was always a tone shift when
OL,10,Ftheir names were mentioned to the
OL,11,Fadults around me. The same adoration
OL,12,Fwe reserved for professional players
OL,13,Fwasn't granted to them.
OL,15,FAlways inquisitive, I'd ask why
OL,16,Fweren't they celebrated?
OL,18,F"Well, because they went to league",
OL,19,FI'd be told.
