OL,3,CDoes rugby union owe rugby league an
OL,4,Capology?
OL,6,FRugby league was a foreign term to me,
OL,7,Fbut I could sense there was a
OL,8,Ffrostiness towards it. That's about
OL,9,Fthe extent of explanation anyone was
OL,10,Fwilling to give a 10-year-old. Over
OL,11,Ftime I learned more about these rugby
OL,12,Frebels, and somehow seemed to
OL,13,Funderstand them being outcast less.
OL,15,FWhy did it matter if they were paid to
OL,16,Fplay? That seemed to be why the likes
OL,17,Fof Doddie Weir were loved by the same
OL,18,Fpeople. What was the big deal about
OL,19,Fswitching codes? After all, Alan Tait
OL,20,Fhad done it. Twice.
