OL,6,FProfessional pariahs
OL,8,FUpon signing for a league team,
OL,9,Fcodebreakers found those who had
OL,10,Fcheered on the tryline for them would
OL,11,Fturn away in the streets.
OL,13,FIt just didn't make sense, and so I
OL,14,Fbegan digging deeper. I got in touch
OL,15,Fwith various border codebreakers from
OL,16,Fthe 1960s, 70s and 80s, who left us to
OL,17,Fhave their talents rewarded and ended
OL,18,Fup paying a heavy cost.
