OL,3,CDoes rugby union owe rugby league an
OL,4,Capology?
OL,6,FTo the untrained eye it's all rugby -
OL,7,Fthe same posts, same shaped ball, the
OL,8,Fsame rugged physicality - but
OL,9,Ftechnically the games are so
OL,10,Fdifferent, as is the social fabric
OL,11,Fsurrounding them. But the talent of
OL,12,Fthese codebreakers cannot be
OL,13,Funderstated. To switch games they had
OL,14,Fto have great skill, as well as the
OL,15,Fdetermination to adapt to a whole new
OL,16,Fgame.
