OL,3,CDoes rugby union owe rugby league an
OL,4,Capology?
OL,6,FTake Ron Cowan, a key player for his
OL,7,Fhome side of Selkirk and the Scotland
OL,8,Fsquad of the early 1960s. By 18 he
OL,9,Fbecame the youngest Scot to ever tour
OL,10,Fwith the British and Irish lions. Any
OL,11,Fborder rugby town would celebrate a
OL,12,Fcareer like this for generations to
OL,13,Fcome.
OL,15,FBut instead, switching to play rugby
OL,16,Fleague for Leeds was seen as betrayal,
OL,17,Fand meant his accolades were
OL,18,Funderstated. In fact, they were
OL,19,Foverwritten. Discarded altogether.
OL,21,FWhy defy the church?
