OL,6,FBut league teams were often based in
OL,7,Fareas with strong textile industries,
OL,8,Fso it was also an easy move to make
OL,9,Fgeographically, culturally and
OL,10,Fsocially.
OL,12,FHe theorised border codebreakers may
OL,13,Fhave had more in common with the
OL,14,Fworking class players of rugby league
OL,15,Fsquads, than the well connected
OL,16,Fprivately educated players from the
OL,17,Fcentral belt who dominated the
OL,18,FScotland team.
