OL,6,FBut rugby league scouts also
OL,7,Fpurposefully sought out border
OL,8,Fplayers. The Borders is of course the
OL,9,Fhome of rugby sevens - union's faster
OL,10,Fpaced younger sibling. It's a game
OL,11,Fwith fewer players and stoppages, and
OL,12,Fhas created generations of agile,
OL,13,Fskillful players perfect for poaching.
OL,14,FWith a tournament every weekend in the
OL,15,Fsevens season, it was the perfect
OL,16,Fscouting ground to find talent to
OL,17,Ftempt to switch.
