OL,3,CDoes rugby union owe rugby league an
OL,4,Capology?
OL,6,FThe treatment of codebreakers has been
OL,7,Fa topic long kept off the table. For
OL,8,Fmany players the way union disregarded
OL,9,Fwhat they had achieved before
OL,10,Fswitching was so hurtful, they
OL,11,Fthemselves began to neglect
OL,12,Facknowledging their rugby roots.
OL,14,FRon Cowan's daughter didn't even know
OL,15,Fhe had played rugby - the sport that
OL,16,Fdefined much of his life - until she
OL,17,Fwas 12 years old. But he wasn't alone.
OL,18,FPlayers who should be icons to us
OL,19,Fborderers became exiles, and I can't
OL,20,Fhelp but feel previous generations
OL,21,Ffailed them.
