OL,6,FIt's an entirely different landscape
OL,7,Ftoday. Louis Rees-Zammit fled to an
OL,8,Fentirely different sport in America
OL,9,Fbefore he returned to rugby to be
OL,10,Fwelcomed with open arms when his love
OL,11,Ffor rugby rekindled. His brief
OL,12,Fdisappearance already fading from fans
OL,13,Fmemories. While the knowledge and
OL,14,Fexpertise of former league players is
OL,15,Fnow relied on at the top of the modern
OL,16,Funion game.
