OL,3,CDoes rugby union owe rugby league an
OL,4,Capology?
OL,6,FA Scottish Rugby Union spokesperson
OL,7,Fsaid: "History cannot be rewritten,
OL,8,Fbut rugby union has changed
OL,9,Fsignificantly in the last 30 years
OL,10,Fsince it became a professional sport.
OL,11,FWe are hugely proud to celebrate the
OL,12,Fachievements of Ronnie Cowan and those
OL,13,Fwho trod a similar path. Ronnie has
OL,14,Fbeen a regular spectator at Scotland
OL,15,Finternational matches at Murrayfield
OL,16,Fup to this decade and he will always
OL,17,Fbe warmly welcomed by Scottish Rugby."
